"External data parallel (`external_dp_template` / `external_dp_launch` / "
"`external_dp_proxy`)"
msgstr "外部数据并行 (`external_dp_template` / `external_dp_launch` / `external_dp_proxy`)"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/doc_writing.md:143
msgid ""
"These three converters read one **shared** external-DP YAML (see "
"`tests/e2e/nightly/multi_node/external_dp/config/`) and each render a "
"different part of the deployment. They are tightly coupled to that schema"
" by design."
msgstr ""
"这三个转换器读取一个**共享**的外部DP YAML（参见 `tests/e2e/nightly/multi_node/external_dp/config/`），每个转换器渲染部署的不同部分。它们设计上与那个模式紧密耦合。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/doc_writing.md:147
msgid "The shared YAML provides:"
msgstr "共享 YAML 提供："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/doc_writing.md:149
msgid "`model`: model name (top level)"
msgstr "`model`：模型名称（顶层）"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/doc_writing.md:150
msgid ""
"`config`: a list of per-node settings (`port_start`, `dp_rpc_port`, "
"`dp_size`, `dp_size_local`, `dp_rank_start`, `tp_size`, `dp_address`, "
"...)"
msgstr "`config`：每个节点设置的列表（`port_start`、`dp_rpc_port`、`dp_size`、`dp_size_local`、`dp_rank_start`、`tp_size`、`dp_address` 等）"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/doc_writing.md:152
msgid ""
"`routing`: `type` plus `groups` (e.g. `prefiller` / `decoder` lists of "
"`config` indices)"
msgstr "`routing`：`type` 加上 `groups`（例如 `prefiller` / `decoder` 的 `config` 索引列表）"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/doc_writing.md:153
msgid "`templates`: a list of per-node `envs` and `server_cmd_template` entries"
msgstr "`templates`：每个节点的 `envs` 和 `server_cmd_template` 条目列表"

