#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/doc_writing.md:172
msgid "Templates"
msgstr "模板"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/doc_writing.md:183
msgid ""
"`external_dp_launch` (one `python launch_online_dp.py ...` line per "
"`config` node) and `external_dp_proxy` (the load-balance proxy command, "
"e.g. `python load_balance_proxy_server_example.py ...`) read the whole "
"cluster, so they take **no** index option:"
msgstr ""
"`external_dp_launch`（每个`config`节点对应一行`python launch_online_dp.py ...`）和`external_dp_proxy`（负载均衡代理命令，例如`python load_balance_proxy_server_example.py ...`）读取整个集群，因此它们**不**接受索引选项："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/doc_writing.md:24
msgid "One of `external_dp_template`, `external_dp_launch`, `external_dp_proxy`"
msgstr "`external_dp_template`、`external_dp_launch`、`external_dp_proxy`之一"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/doc_writing.md:24
msgid "`external_dp_template` only"
msgstr "仅`external_dp_template`"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/doc_writing.md:24
msgid "Use `templates[host_index]` from the YAML as the rendering source"
msgstr "使用YAML中的`templates[host_index]`作为渲染源"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/doc_writing.md:214
msgid ""
"`external_dp_proxy` currently supports only `routing.type: "
"disaggregated_prefill` and reads its `routing.groups.prefiller` / "
"`routing.groups.decoder` node lists."
msgstr ""
"`external_dp_proxy`当前仅支持`routing.type: disaggregated_prefill`，并读取其`routing.groups.prefiller`/`routing.groups.decoder`节点列表。"

